#

Spicy Guacamole with Jalapeños

10 min
$5
200 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Mexican

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

AppetizerSnackEasy

Description

A zesty and creamy guacamole with a spicy kick from fresh jalapeños, perfect for dipping or topping.

Ingredients

  • ripe avocados: 2
  • fresh lime juice: 2 tablespoons
  • jalapeños: 1, diced
  • red onion: 1/4, finely chopped
  • cilantro: 2 tablespoons, chopped
  • salt: 1/2 teaspoon
  • black pepper: to taste
